REQUIRED DEPENDENCIES

MPI
PETSc (development version)
pythia
spatialdata
  proj
numpy
FIAT
nemesis
SWIG (if building from repository)

OPTIONAL DEPENDENCIES

cppunit
HDF5
CUBIT
  netcdf
PETSc (development version) w/ParMetis
  git (if building from repository)
